channel.title: I can't add any more GlobalObjects?
channel.description:
Hey guy's, I'm having a major problem because if I want to release my server soon, I will have to keep adding objects. I'm using [i]FunScap3[/i] as my source incase you need to know. What happened was that one day I was adding objects and one object didn't work. Then I thought I must have screwed something up or got the coords wrong. But I tried to fix and logged back on, nothing. Then I took a break from coding my server for a while (about a week) and I was just adding a new Thieving Area. I was writing down coords and stuff and went down to AddGlobalObject and added what I wanted. Saved, Compiled, Ran, and nothing was added. I tried again and it didn't work. And I tried like three times before I got worried.
So now my question is this, WHAT IT WRONG! Lol, I really need to know because I'm trying to release my server for download on Halloween or the week of Halloween. Someone please help! Thanks!
- I Fix I
